    <div class="h2">A $300 bag shouldn't need replacing to feel new.</div>
    <p>Charmé is a small studio making elevated clip-on charms — the kind that make the bag you already love feel new again. No plastic-toy look. No fake heritage. Just one good little object, shipped fast.</p>
