<section class="story-body">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="cols">
      <div class="prose">
        <p>We started Charmé for a simple reason: the bag charm trend was everywhere, but almost all of it looked like a plastic toy clipped to a real handbag. The gap was obvious — people wanted the fun of switching up their bag without the cheap finish that cheapened everything around it.</p>
        <p>So we focused on one thing and did it properly: a weighted metal-and-enamel charm that feels like it belongs on a bag you actually paid for. One clip, endless moods. Designed to be swapped, gifted, and shown off.</p>
        <p>We're a small operation, so we keep it honest: real photos, clear shipping windows, and no invented family saga. We ship fast, we answer our email, and we'd rather sell you one charm you love than five you forget in a drawer.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="story-vis"><div class="charm-badge"><svg viewBox="0 0 120 120"><use href="#charm"/></svg></div><div class="slot-note">Image slot · story 1080×1350</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="values">
      <div class="value"><b>Elevated, not cheap</b><p>Metal and enamel over hollow plastic — the finish is the whole point.</p></div>
      <div class="value"><b>Honest by default</b><p>Real photos, real delivery windows, real reviews. No dark patterns.</p></div>
      <div class="value"><b>Small and fast</b><p>A studio, not a warehouse empire. Orders ship in 1–2 days.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

